#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "&picmi; is a single player puzzle game."
msgstr "&picmi; je igra ugank za enega igralca."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "&picmi; gameboard"
msgstr "&picmi; igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal of the game is to color cells according to numbers given at the "
"side of the board."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je pobarvati celice glede na številke, ki so podane ob strani "
"plošče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player is presented with a blank board, and a list of numbers for each "
"row and column. These numbers represent how runs are organized within any "
"given row or column. For example, a number sequence of <quote>4 8 3</quote> "
"would mean there are sets of four, eight, and three filled cells, in that "
"order, with at least one blank cell between successive groups. The objective "
"of the game is to use these hints to uncover the actual solution, and do "
"this as quickly as possible."
msgstr ""
"Igralec ima prazno tablo in seznam številk za vsako vrstico in stolpec. Te "
"številke predstavljajo, kako so zagoni organizirani v kateri koli vrstici "
"ali stolpcu. Na primer, številsko zaporedje <quote>4 8 3</quote> bi "
"pomenilo, da obstajajo nizi štirih, osmih in treh zapolnjenih celic v tem "
"vrstnem redu, z vsaj eno prazno celico med zaporednimi skupinami. Cilj igre "
"je s pomočjo teh namigov odkriti dejansko rešitev, in to čim hitreje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A left-click (un)marks a cell as occupied, while a right click (un)marks a "
"cell as empty. Dragging may be used to mark several cells in a row or column "
"in one go. The elapsed time is displayed in the status bar, and an overview "
"of the game board is located in the upper left corner. A game is completed "
"once all occupied cells have been marked correctly."
msgstr ""
"Levi klik (od)označi celico kot zasedeno, medtem ko desni klik (od)označi "
"celico kot prazno. Z vlečenjem lahko naenkrat označite več celic v vrstici "
"ali stolpcu. V statusni vrstici je prikazan pretečeni čas, v zgornjem levem "
"kotu pa je pregled igralne plošče. Igra je končana, ko so vse zasedene "
"celice pravilno označene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current placement of boxes and crosses (referred to as 'states' from now "
"on) can be saved at any time. Saving a new state does not overwrite previous "
"saved states. Restoring a state always returns to the most recently saved "
"state. This can be repeated until no more saved states remain. The number of "
"actions since the latest saved state is displayed in the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Trenutna postavitev polj in križcev (odslej imenovana 'stanja') lahko kadar "
"koli shranite. Shranjevanje novega stanja ne prepiše prejšnjih shranjenih "
"stanj. Obnovitev stanja se vedno vrne v nazadnje shranjeno stanje. To lahko "
"ponavljate, dokler ne ostane nobeno shranjeno stanje. Število dejanj od "
"zadnjega shranjenega stanja je prikazano v vrstici stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&picmi; includes two game modes. Random puzzles (generated by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item) are generated according to the selected difficulty "
"settings. Alternatively, the included preset puzzles can be played by "
"selecting the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&picmi; vključuje dva načina igre. Naključne uganke (generirane z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem> Nov</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menijski element) se ustvarijo glede na izbrane "
"nastavitve težavnosti. Druga možnost je, da vključene prednastavljene uganke "
"igrate tako, da izberete element menija <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number sequence in a row or column provides certain information about "
"the count of occupied cells and their arrangement within a row or column."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedje številk v vrstici ali stolpcu zagotavlja določene informacije o "
"številu zasedenih celic in njihovi razporeditvi v vrstici ali stolpcu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number represents the length of a connected run of occupied cells on the "
"board. This run either has at least one empty cell on each side or is "
"located directly on the board edge."
msgstr ""
"Število predstavlja dolžino povezanega zaporedja zasedenih celic na plošči. "
"Ta niz ima vsaj eno prazno celico na vsaki strani ali pa se nahaja "
"neposredno na robu plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, a number sequence shows the order of these runs within a row "
"or column."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega številčno zaporedje prikazuje vrstni red teh izvajanj v vrstici "
"ali stolpcu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option applies only to games with "
"<guimenu>Custom</guimenu> difficulty."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Preprečuj napake:</guilabel> velja samo za igre s "
"težavnostjo <guimenu>Po meri</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is enabled, it is not "
"possible to incorrectly mark a cell as occupied - instead, penalty time is "
"added to the timer. The penalty is increased with each mistake made."
msgstr ""
"Ko je možnost <guilabel>Preprečevanje napak:</guilabel> omogočena, celice ni "
"mogoče nepravilno označiti kot zasedeno - namesto tega se časovniku doda "
"kazenski čas. Kazen se poveča z vsako storjeno napako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is disabled, there is no "
"feedback whether a cell has been marked correctly, and there is no penalty "
"for making mistakes."
msgstr ""
"Če je možnost <guilabel>Preprečevanje napak:</guilabel> onemogočena, ni "
"povratne informacije, ali je bila celica pravilno označena, in ni kazni za "
"napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game will stop once all occupied cells have been marked correctly."
msgstr "Igra se bo ustavila, ko bodo vse zasedene celice pravilno označene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Starts a new game.</action> It creates a random board using the "
"current difficulty level."
msgstr ""
"<action>Začne novo igro.</action> Ustvari naključno tablo z uporabo trenutne "
"težavnostne stopnje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Loads a preset puzzle.</action> The names of puzzles are hidden "
"until they are solved. High score lists and difficulty settings are disabled."
msgstr ""
"<action>Naloži prednastavljeno uganko.</action> Imena ugank so skrita, "
"dokler niso rešena. Seznami najboljših rezultatov in nastavitve težavnosti "
"so onemogočeni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Restart Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Znova zaženi igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will restart the current game."
msgstr "To bo znova zagnalo trenutno igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Pauses the game time.</action> Click on the menu item again to make "
"the game resume. Note that the board disappears when the game is paused as "
"it would be unfair if you could search for good moves without the time "
"pressure."
msgstr ""
"<action>Začasno ustavi čas igre.</action> Znova kliknite element menija, da "
"se igra nadaljuje. Upoštevajte, da tabla izgine, ko je igra začasno "
"ustavljena, saj bi bilo nepošteno, če bi lahko iskali dobre poteze brez "
"časovnega pritiska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores…</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a dialog containing the High Scores for the various difficulty levels."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno z najboljšimi rezultati za različne težavnostne "
"stopnje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> the &picmi;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &picmi;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Undo the previous move</action> if one exists."
msgstr "<action>Razveljavi prejšnji premik</action>, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marks a cell as occupied or empty."
msgstr "Označi celico kot zasedeno ali prazno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Solve</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play a demo game."
msgstr "Igrajte demo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load Position</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži položaj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loads the most recently saved position."
msgstr "Naloži nazadnje shranjen položaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Position</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani položaj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the current board position."
msgstr "Shrani trenutni položaj plošče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Celozaslonski "
"način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the graphic interface to full screen mode."
msgstr "Preklopi grafični vmesnik v celozaslonski način."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lets you set the difficulty level from a sub-menu."
msgstr "Omogoča nastavitev težavnostne stopnje iz podmenija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are four levels of difficulty:"
msgstr "Obstajajo štiri težavnostne stopnje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Easy</guimenuitem>: 10 rows, 10 columns, 55% of all cells are "
"occupied, <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is disabled."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Enostavno</guimenuitem>: 10 vrstic, 10 stolpcev, 55 % vseh "
"celic je zasedenih, <guilabel>Prepreči napake:</guilabel> možnost je "
"onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem>: 10 rows, 15 columns, 55% of all cells are "
"occupied, <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is disabled."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Srednje</guimenuitem>: 10 vrstic, 15 stolpcev, 55 % vseh celic "
"je zasedenih, <guilabel>Prepreči napake:</guilabel> možnost je onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>: 15 rows, 15 columns, 55% of all cells are "
"occupied, <guilabel>Prevent mistakes:</guilabel> option is disabled."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Težko</guimenuitem>: 15 vrstic, 15 stolpcev, 55 % vseh celic je "
"zasedenih, <guilabel>Prepreči napake:</guilabel> možnost je onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem>: Custom board dimensions and settings."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Po meri</guimenuitem>: Mere in nastavitve plošče po meri."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &picmi;…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &picmi;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the game background image, board dimensions and settings for custom "
"difficulty."
msgstr ""
"Izberite sliko ozadja igre, dimenzije plošče in nastavitve za težavnost po "
"meri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &picmi; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &picmi; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:227 index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default shortcuts are:"
msgstr "Privzete bližnjice so:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start a new game"
msgstr "Začni novo igro"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:237
